state.unicode: Below is a list of existing public Steam Groups which operate as clans in Shogun 2. You can join any of these groups by selecting it from the list and clicking the "Go To Steam Group Page" button. This will bring up the group's page in Steam where you can opt to join the group.
Once you have joined the group it will appear in the list to the left, and you can opt to label it as your Shogun 2 clan.
